      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The photograph shows the exterior of the newly established ‘Boyana’ film studios in Sofia. The studios are situated on the fringes of Sofia on undeveloped land.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The ‘Boyana’ film studios in Sofia opened in 1962 and comprised all facilities for full film production. Boyana Film was the main site of film production during the communist era when Bulgarian cinema was at its peak.</ab>
